### Listar etapas
GET http://localhost:3002/etapas

### Buscar etapa por id
GET http://localhost:3002/etapas/1

### Criar etapa
POST http://localhost:3002/etapas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Etapa Inicial",
  "diaId": 1
}

### Atualizar etapa
PUT http://localhost:3002/etapas/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Etapa Avançada"
}

### Deletar etapa
DELETE http://localhost:3002/etapas/1
